  "detailed_description": "<strong>History</strong><br>A dark evil spreads across the Hayabusa region. A clan of shadow ninjas, led by the fearsome Ryujin, advances, casting darkness over peaceful villages. Peace is threatened, and darkness spreads.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2588430/extras/b37f1d5c08cca051882de5c687f466bd.avif?t=1728840682\" width=640 height=360 /></span><br>Embark on a journey to defeat Shadow Clan and restore peace to Hayabusa.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2588430/extras/5bc7886df23416831fada252233dffa7.avif?t=1728840682\" width=640 height=360 /></span><br><strong>You control a young ninja named Takeshi.</strong><br>• Face skilled ninjas and monsters.<br>• Explore the Hayabusa region.<br>• Discover dangerous dungeons.<br>• Protect other villages from ninjas.<br>• Defeat the shadow clan.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2588430/extras/d37e48ea9284893ff5854c4e5148ccb0.avif?t=1728840682\" width=720 height=404 /></span>",
